1. Ti *hodaš* svakog dana. (You *walk* every day.)
2. On *hoda* jako brzo. (He *walks* very fast.)
3. Oni *hodaju* pored reke. (They *are walking* next to the river.)
4. Ja ne mogu da *hodam* bez cipela. (I can't *walk* without shoes.)
5. Da li *hodaš* po kiši? (Do you *walk* in the rain?)
6. Oni *hodaju* zajedno svake nedelje. (They *walk* together every week.)
7. Kako *hodaš* u novim cipelama? (How do you *walk* in new shoes?)
8. Ja *hodam* do posla svaki dan. (I *walk* to work every day.)
9. Oni *hodaju* po parku. (They *walk* in the park.)
10. Ti *hodaš* jako sporo danas. (You *walk* very slowly today.)